; Coverage for report.cc line 819: fn_truncated with string value (no width arg)
; When truncated() is called on a string without a width, it falls through
; to format_t::truncate with width=0 (no truncation)

2024/01/01 Test Long Payee Name
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --format "%(truncated(payee))\n"
Test Long Payee Name
end test
